metadata.name: Rebirth
metadata.description:
With the end of one personality another comes into the world; This can be compared to lighting a new candle with the flame of a dying candle. The consciousness of the reborn person is neither identical nor completely different from the consciousness of the deceased; but a causal continuity or flow can be mentioned.

Used Programs : Adobe Photoshop , 3ds Max

Dimensions: 1181X1181
